title: What is the initial password of the M635 and how to change the initial passwordï¼Ÿ
answer:
The initial password of the M635 is the last four letters of the Mobile Directory Number (MDN).  
By default, the phone lock is not enabled. The default phone lock code can be changed to any string of one to eight digits. To change the phone lock code, select Menu -> Settings -> Security -> Change Phone Lock Code. After the phone lock is enabled, each time you powers on the phone, the phone displays "Enter Phone Lock Code". In this case, enter the correct phone lock code to use the phone normally. Otherwise, you can only make emergency calls. When the code is forgotten, contact the after-sale service center of the operator.
